{"tid":1271131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[現場] 煲底發夢開會 整合","createTime":"2019-07-01T05:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T05:34:47.000Z","uid":126153,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b405d81c532c8b9fe035fbebcd992288a196c0c8","tid":1271131,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"大約12:30pm煲底現場開左大會表態<br />\n討論現場接住落黎要點做 有咩方向<br />\n圍繞兩樣野: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[black]地點 時間[/black]</span><br />\n地點有四個地方:<br />\n1. 立會+政總<br />\n2. 金紫荊<br />\n3. 紅磡<br />\n4. 禮賓府<br />\n現場最後大多數支持 1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立會+政總</span></span><br />\n時間 一直有爭議 有在場勇武派支持依家<br />\n亦有人propose 三點/四點/五點<br />\n總之就係依家vs 等遊行隊伍到達<br />\n時間無明顯共識 但有現場人士已開始準備<br />\n煲底外都慢慢收到風要攻立會 有人鼓躁有人屌<br />\n大致係咁<br />\n依家在場手足準備緊 唔知大家支持定反對<br />\n但個勢係一定會攻<br />\n<br />\n以上整合 以下個人意見<br />\n現場好多手足琴晚今朝就出黎 物資嚴重短缺 除左水<br />\n下奏黎遊行既 唔該買小小物資入黎支持前線<br />\n主要三樣野: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3m口罩 頭盔 遮/小型防衛工具</span></span><br />\n現場做既決定 希望大家唔好屌<br />\n講過好多次 勇武和理非係可以一齊做<br />\n只要有人有物資backup 一切不是夢<br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"afbe26566fd771d26eb602ba9bbff2f301c5ba00","tid":1271131,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1f920a9642baddef26e4ca52eac4addfd337f7","tid":1271131,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"我係港島區總指揮部，多謝提供消息"},{"pid":"b9ca1663a5fb18664ec0ccc12f39397e7393ae89","tid":1271131,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"自推 唔要互屌 唔好分化 互相支持"},{"pid":"eae53e1943e4231d0625c7f3771c68b1b9e98d06","tid":1271131,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b3b493eb480c87da39d684f21ff47c2e20ee7a","tid":1271131,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"禮賓府啦！"},{"pid":"fbdaa28d14efe689b94e3181ab6e7b1174d88196","tid":1271131,"uid":4645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"已經衝緊"},{"pid":"475c113fdb91a40cb7462ac0fd4234defba6276a","tid":1271131,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b2ef98eed765c84e691936d19e20ec15d73f1b","tid":1271131,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"衝入去做乜鳩？"},{"pid":"c076528538a1e52c9cfaf69ccd234eed82419ebd","tid":1271131,"uid":52836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8d153c5b2d7dd6e57d9268be2d626077255763","tid":1271131,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"尊重現場決定<br />\n但個人認為暑假前攻立會無咩實興意義"},{"pid":"fbb5d6ab9543050a0993bdd448d4dfe2ce282bed","tid":1271131,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d8d153c5b2d7dd6e57d9268be2d626077255763","tid":1271131,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"尊重現場決定<br />\n但個人認為暑假前攻立會無咩實興意義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"質*"},{"pid":"28afc65ddf5d8554a815891b90c99163b2861292","tid":1271131,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"最新更新 已經衝緊玻璃"},{"pid":"eb6b458042f2dbacb39374c3f035de505975dd0f","tid":1271131,"uid":147485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n最緊要目標明確<br />\n唔係要落佢面 而係要做到4大訴求呀<br />\